s.com/realtimenews/20160412003089-260404|accessdate=2016-04-12|date=2016-04-13|archive-date=2019-02-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190227182133/https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20160412003089-260404|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=【拍GV因禍得福】 小林竜介飛返日本 獲有心人爭住合作|url=http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20160411/54974218|accessdate=2016-04-11|date=2016-04-13|archive-date=2016-07-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160718011835/http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/enews/realtime/20160411/54974218|dead-url=no}}</ref>。當小林龍介再度開啟[[Instagram|Instagram]]後，他上傳三段影片中解釋自己為何要關閉，並於影片中講述他的行蹤和對未來的想法，也承諾會回到中国大陸与香港演藝圈<ref>{{cite news|title=（有片）拍GV片斷送星途 男星振作「我會回來！」|url=http://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/1665773|accessdate=2016-04-15|date=2016-04-17|archive-date=2019-02-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190228004335/https://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/1665773|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=小林龍介GV片被瘋傳　首出面用3段影片解釋原因|url=http://star.ettoday.net/news/681310|accessdate=2016-04-15|date=2016-04-17|archive-date=2019-02-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190227182016/https://star.ettoday.net/news/681310|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=拍GV斷星路 小林龍介憔悴喊話：別擔心我|url=http://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20160415005290-260404|accessdate=2016-04-15|date=2016-04-17|archive-date=2019-02-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190227182118/https://www.chinatimes.com/realtimenews/20160415005290-260404|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2017年轉往[[泰國|泰國]]發展演藝事業<ref>{{cite news|title=（專訪）男星拍同志色情片遭解約 前戰友透露他去向|url=http://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/2079605|accessdate=2017-05-26|date=2017-06-04|archive-date=2017-05-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170526004249/http://ent.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/2079605|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

